2011-12-07T14:43:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-07/mechel-adrs-reiterated-buy-by-otkritie-brokerage-in-moscow.html
Otkritie brokerage reiterated its
“buy” recommendation on  OAO Mechel (MTL) ,  Russia ’s largest producer
of steel-making coal. The 12-month target price is unchanged at
$16.60, analyst Denis Gabrielik said via telephone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
